{"tid":2428793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"登登又發明新招，對沙地皇子『保留制裁權利』，真係嚇撚死人 [sosad]","createTime":"2021-03-01T22:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T00:18:02.000Z","uid":130105,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0d9317f3afe804af80dbe7ff2d3c76bed24c96","tid":2428793,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T22:16:26.000Z","msg":"講咗成個星期，以為會出乜重手，真係人唔笑，狗都吠<br />\n===========================================<br />\n&bull; Jen Psaki said Joe Biden 'reserves the right' to sanction Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman for U.S-based journalist Jamal Khashoggi's murder<br />\n&bull;'We reserve the right to take any action at a time and manner of our choosing,' Biden's press secretary told reporters on Monday <br />\n&bull;She added: 'Our objective is to recalibrate the relationship, prevent this from ever happening again and to find ways to work together with Saudi leadership'<br />\n&bull;Biden said Saturday that he would make an announcement regarding Saudi Arabia on Monday after receiving criticism for not being hard enough on MBS<br />\n&bull;A U.S. intelligence report concluded the de facto Saudi ruler approved the October 2018 killing of Khashoggi &ndash; a Washington Post columnist critical of MBS<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2021/03/01/20/39919356-9314045-image-a-1_1614630428699.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F20%2F39919356-9314045-image-a-1_1614630428699.jpg&h=1e445d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n White House Press Secretary Jen Psaki on Monday said President Joe Biden 'reserves the right' to sanction Saudi Crown Prince Mohammed bin Salman for U.S-based journalist Jamal Khashoggi's murder<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2021/03/01/20/39919248-9314045-image-a-2_1614630446618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F20%2F39919248-9314045-image-a-2_1614630446618.jpg&h=8b2128a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Biden said Saturday that he would make an announcement regarding Saudi Arabia on Monday which has yet to come<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2021/03/01/20/39919234-9314045-image-a-3_1614630449569.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F20%2F39919234-9314045-image-a-3_1614630449569.jpg&h=130a5570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n A U.S. intelligence report concluded the de facto Saudi ruler (pictured on Saturday) was behind the killing of Khashoggi<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2021/03/01/20/39919214-9314045-image-a-6_1614630734114.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F20%2F39919214-9314045-image-a-6_1614630734114.jpg&h=a7949597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n Khashoggi, who wrote opinion columns for the Washington Post critical of MBS, was killed and dismembered inside the Saudi consulate in Istanbul, Turkey in October 2018. MBS has denied any involvement in his murder<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/1s/2021/03/01/20/39919838-9314045-image-a-16_1614631284982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2F1s%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F20%2F39919838-9314045-image-a-16_1614631284982.jpg&h=9d8ddbc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n The Biden administration has received harsh criticism for not being hard enough on MBS  in particular for not issuing sanctions after the intelligence report found he most likely had to give 'approval' for Khashoggi's killing to happen<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2021/03/01/749821737762965863/1024x576_MP4_749821737762965863.mp4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideos.dailymail.co.uk%2Fvideo%2Fmol%2F2021%2F03%2F01%2F749821737762965863%2F1024x576_MP4_749821737762965863.mp4&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt18v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=25b6658d\" target=\"_blank\">https://videos.dailymail.co.uk/video/mol/2021/03/01/749821737762965863/1024x576_MP4_749821737762965863.mp4</a><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9314045/Joe-Biden-reserves-right-sanction-Saudis-crown-prince-MBS-future-White-House-says.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-9314045%2FJoe-Biden-reserves-right-sanction-Saudis-crown-prince-MBS-future-White-House-says.html&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt18v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=99e4d7fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-9314045/Joe-Biden-reserves-right-sanction-Saudis-crown-prince-MBS-future-White-House-says.html</a>"},{"pid":"f1eb6c0ec49dfa4047a11e866542654fa55c0da3","tid":2428793,"uid":253016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T22:18:24.000Z","msg":"好撚驚呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"0fd1cff2bf36bc5d48ff4028c833b4617d031134","tid":2428793,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T22:19:19.000Z","msg":"對沙地硬了<br />\n對香港不了"},{"pid":"e0e5f96957d56853991e201827e9cef9cc7bd247","tid":2428793,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T22:28:05.000Z","msg":"同中國打飛機式口技有咩分別？"},{"pid":"438f90b38e2fa0cbdf1bdc68b8a51a6703ab7538","tid":2428793,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T23:00:07.000Z","msg":"無辦法，美國唔可以無咗沙特。所以要美國甚至西方保你一定要佢地了解保你會有咩利益。<br />\n<br />\n香港利益所在就係亞洲買辦，因為中國想係香港玩晒西方先會出聲。香港真正有民主自由就係對西方既投資嚟講最安全保證。<br />\n<br />\n西方唔係戇鳩，本來香港島係永屬英國，而九龍新界就係要還比中華民國。中華民國並未滅國而去咗台灣。所以先可以理直氣壯。"},{"pid":"fc8955cba35339e16d88e19c45afdd18c3766abb","tid":2428793,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T23:06:50.000Z","msg":"殺本國公民 - 無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eebb511c982ba7221f5a63f4600492295e92346","tid":2428793,"uid":61589,"like":7,"dislike":8,